## Миграции PostgreSQL

```sql
-- 001_init: users, api_keys, memory_instances (type IN rag/wiki/episodic/working/graph/reflective), usage_log
-- 002_pgvector: rag_chunks (embedding vector(3072)), rag_topics, rag_topic_chunks
-- 003_concepts: sources, segments (embedding), concepts (state, confidence, bi-temporal valid_from/valid_until, embedding),
--               evidence_spans (concept_id→source_id→segment_id), concept_relations (typed),
--               mentions (staging, consolidated_concept_id nullable, router_decision),
--               residuals (rejected mentions for offline analysis)
-- 004_episodic: episodic_memories (decay_weight, bi-temporal valid_from/valid_until)
-- 005_working: working_memory (session_id, key, value JSONB, expires_at, UNIQUE(instance,session,key))
-- 006_graph_age: CREATE EXTENSION age; -- graphs created dynamically per instance
-- 007_reflective: user_reactions (state from controlled vocabulary of 12 values,
--                 intensity float, valence, epistemic_status explicit/inferred,
--                 evidence_source_id, topic_concept_id)
-- 008_action_log: action_log (actor, action, target_concept_id, rationale, evidence_ids)
-- 009_gardener: gardener_proposals (type, candidate_ids, status pending/approved/rejected/executed),
--              repair_queue (concept_id, reason, priority, status)
```

Key constraints:
- concepts.confidence CHECK (0..1), capped by evidence
- concepts.state IN (active, weak, merged, split, archived, stale, disputed)
- user_reactions.state IN (frustration, anxiety, exhaustion, clarity, inspiration, joy, confusion, neutral, determination, overwhelmed, insight, other)
- user_reactions.epistemic_status IN (explicit, inferred) — модель ОБЯЗАНА различать наблюдаемое и интерпретируемое
- Reflective concepts (behavioral_pattern, tension) создаются ТОЛЬКО при ≥3 cross-episode evidence

